1
00:01:33,239 --> 00:01:34,319
Greetings, Your Majesty.

2
00:01:34,920 --> 00:01:35,640
Rise.

3
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:36,879
Thank you, Your Majesty.

4
00:01:38,920 --> 00:01:40,280
Did We tell you to rise?

5
00:01:41,920 --> 00:01:43,680
Kneeling again? What's going on?

6
00:01:46,359 --> 00:01:47,040
Ning Chen.

7
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:48,319
We have a question for you.

8
00:01:48,799 --> 00:01:51,040
Is this Music Bureau really that fun?

9
00:01:51,760 --> 00:01:52,760
Your Majesty, didn't you say you wouldn't interfere

10
00:01:52,879 --> 00:01:54,519
with the Imperial Inspectorate going to the Music Bureau?

11
00:01:54,879 --> 00:01:56,239
Why are you giving me a hard time?

12
00:01:56,959 --> 00:01:57,480
It's fun, of course.

13
00:02:00,959 --> 00:02:02,239
Then tell Us about it.

14
00:02:02,560 --> 00:02:03,719
How exactly is it fun?

15
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:05,120
Just how much fun is it?

16
00:02:05,599 --> 00:02:06,120
Your Majesty,

17
00:02:06,959 --> 00:02:08,240
at the Music Bureau,

18
00:02:08,639 --> 00:02:10,360
I met a girl named Yudie.

19
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:13,120
Her beauty could topple kingdoms,

20
00:02:13,360 --> 00:02:14,840
truly a peerless beauty.

21
00:02:16,800 --> 00:02:18,280
Her temperament is so gentle,

22
00:02:18,759 --> 00:02:21,120
and her voice is so lovely.

23
00:02:21,639 --> 00:02:22,360
And the best part is,

24
00:02:23,039 --> 00:02:24,919
she's the real deal.

25
00:02:25,280 --> 00:02:28,039
But Your Majesty, you...

26
00:02:28,599 --> 00:02:29,199
We what?

27
00:02:32,919 --> 00:02:33,319
Well...

28
00:02:33,599 --> 00:02:34,639
What's with that look?

29
00:02:35,919 --> 00:02:38,639
I feel sorry for Your Majesty.

30
00:02:40,439 --> 00:02:42,919
I think Your Majesty is rather pitiful.

31
00:02:44,360 --> 00:02:45,080
Ridiculous.

32
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:46,639
We rule all under heaven.

33
00:02:46,840 --> 00:02:47,960
What's there to pity?

34
00:02:48,520 --> 00:02:51,400
With a brush, Your Majesty pacifies the realm,

35
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:53,879
and on horseback, you settle the world.

36
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:55,919
Unmatched in both governance and warfare,

37
00:02:56,520 --> 00:02:57,439
your achievements will last forever.

38
00:02:57,800 --> 00:03:00,560
Truly an emperor for the ages,

39
00:03:00,759 --> 00:03:02,159
a peerless wise ruler.

40
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:02,840
The only pity is,

41
00:03:06,599 --> 00:03:08,319
you've never seen a real beauty.

42
00:03:08,759 --> 00:03:09,240
Ning Chen!

43
00:03:09,680 --> 00:03:10,719
Don't talk nonsense.

44
00:03:11,599 --> 00:03:13,280
He's truly talking nonsense.

45
00:03:14,080 --> 00:03:15,800
We have three thousand beauties in Our harem.

46
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:17,280
Which one isn't a beauty?

47
00:03:17,439 --> 00:03:17,960
Your Majesty,

48
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:21,520
what I'm about to say will offend many,

49
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:29,439
but I simply must speak my mind.

50
00:03:30,039 --> 00:03:32,120
When daughters of nobles are sent to the palace,

51
00:03:32,919 --> 00:03:34,360
they have money and connections.

52
00:03:35,080 --> 00:03:37,599
With a few bribes here and there,

53
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:39,879
when Your Majesty picks a tablet each night,

54
00:03:40,039 --> 00:03:40,520
their tablets

55
00:03:40,599 --> 00:03:42,080
just happen to be in the most visible spot.

56
00:03:42,319 --> 00:03:43,599
But those girls from poor families,

57
00:03:43,719 --> 00:03:45,439
some of them are truly beautiful.

58
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:46,599
Just because they have no money,

59
00:03:47,240 --> 00:03:47,759
their tablets

60
00:03:47,840 --> 00:03:49,120
will never reach Your Majesty's eyes.

61
00:03:49,919 --> 00:03:51,240
Even if they grow old and die in the palace,

62
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:53,319
they'll never see Your Majesty their whole lives.

63
00:03:54,960 --> 00:03:55,919
They're done for.

64
00:03:56,479 --> 00:03:58,560
That's how palace dramas always go.

65
00:03:59,159 --> 00:04:01,240
Is what Ning Chen said true?

66
00:04:02,039 --> 00:04:02,599
Your Majesty,

67
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:06,080
this is an unwritten rule of the palace.

68
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:08,159
Then how come We didn't know?

69
00:04:08,840 --> 00:04:10,000
Did you take bribes?

70
00:04:10,960 --> 00:04:12,439
I beg Your Majesty's discernment.

71
00:04:12,479 --> 00:04:14,759
This servant would never dare.

72
00:04:15,039 --> 00:04:17,360
As expected, I'm so clever.

73
00:04:18,519 --> 00:04:18,959
Guards!

74
00:04:19,439 --> 00:04:19,879
Here!

75
00:04:21,079 --> 00:04:21,839
Please calm your anger, Your Majesty.

76
00:04:23,040 --> 00:04:24,120
I think

77
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:25,480
over such a trivial matter,

78
00:04:25,639 --> 00:04:26,920
if Your Majesty harms your royal health out of anger,

79
00:04:27,120 --> 00:04:27,680
it wouldn't be worth it.

80
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:31,639
Why don't I take Your Majesty to the Music Bureau?

81
00:04:31,920 --> 00:04:33,240
The twelve houses of the Music Bureau,

82
00:04:33,319 --> 00:04:35,360
every single girl is as beautiful as a flower.

83
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:36,759
Except for Nanzhi and Yudie, of course.

84
00:04:37,079 --> 00:04:39,240
Your Majesty, take your pick, choose freely.

85
00:04:39,839 --> 00:04:40,519
It's on me.

86
00:04:41,079 --> 00:04:42,639
This kid has lost his mind.

87
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:44,240
You...

88
00:04:45,160 --> 00:04:46,600
What kind of person do you take Us for?

89
00:04:50,279 --> 00:04:51,439
A real man.

90
00:04:53,480 --> 00:04:54,759
Although Your Majesty is the Son of Heaven,

91
00:04:55,199 --> 00:04:57,000
you're also a healthy man.

92
00:04:57,800 --> 00:04:59,800
All of Great Xuan belongs to Your Majesty.

93
00:05:00,079 --> 00:05:02,079
A visit to the Music Bureau isn't too much, is it?

94
00:05:02,839 --> 00:05:03,480
By the way,

95
00:05:04,439 --> 00:05:06,360
Your Majesty wouldn't even need to pay, right?

96
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:08,000
Of course not.

97
00:05:09,120 --> 00:05:11,439
You know, what you're saying makes some sense.

98
00:05:11,879 --> 00:05:13,319
No time like the present.

99
00:05:13,519 --> 00:05:15,600
Let's prepare to depart for the Music Bureau now.

100
00:05:15,759 --> 00:05:16,399
I... I...

101
00:05:22,720 --> 00:05:23,920
Such vulgar words.

102
00:05:25,000 --> 00:05:26,480
No sense of romance.

103
00:05:27,800 --> 00:05:28,319
Your Majesty.

104
00:05:29,480 --> 00:05:31,279
This is a new weapon invented by Ning Chen.

105
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:32,519
It's tremendously powerful.

106
00:05:32,879 --> 00:05:33,800
I came specially to present it to Your Majesty.

107
00:05:34,759 --> 00:05:35,839
What is this thing?

108
00:05:36,279 --> 00:05:36,879
A musket.

109
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:40,680
It fires iron pellets at incredible speed.

110
00:05:41,279 --> 00:05:42,839
I consider my martial skills decent,

111
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:44,720
yet I couldn't even track its movement.

112
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:48,120
We are well aware of your skills.

113
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:51,199
How does it compare to a crossbow?

114
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:52,519
Stronger.

115
00:05:53,160 --> 00:05:53,839
Faster.

116
00:05:56,160 --> 00:05:56,720
Excellent.

117
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:58,839
Then demonstrate it for Us.

118
00:06:00,920 --> 00:06:02,879
Your Majesty, please step outside the hall.

119
00:06:03,279 --> 00:06:04,519
No need. Demonstrate it right here.

120
00:06:40,519 --> 00:06:41,439
How filthy.

121
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:48,360
Then I must trouble Eunuch Quan.

122
00:06:51,639 --> 00:06:52,399
Thank you.

123
00:07:22,839 --> 00:07:24,120
Eunuch Quan, stay your hand!

124
00:07:28,480 --> 00:07:29,120
We are unharmed.

125
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:30,120
Let go.

126
00:07:30,480 --> 00:07:31,040
Let go of me!

127
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:37,759
You wretched eunuch!

128
00:07:38,160 --> 00:07:39,000
Your skills are so impressive.

129
00:07:39,639 --> 00:07:40,600
You've been hiding them well.

130
00:07:41,800 --> 00:07:43,839
Ning Chen wielded a strange object.

131
00:07:43,959 --> 00:07:46,079
He nearly harmed His Majesty!

132
00:07:50,199 --> 00:07:51,959
You made this thing?

133
00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:54,879
Yes.

134
00:07:56,720 --> 00:07:58,399
Come. Let Us take a look.

135
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:06,600
Not that.

136
00:08:07,439 --> 00:08:08,199
Lift your head up.

137
00:08:08,560 --> 00:08:10,000
We want to see your neck.

138
00:08:10,439 --> 00:08:10,920
Come here.

139
00:08:16,839 --> 00:08:18,000
Such a vicious blow.

140
00:08:18,920 --> 00:08:19,720
You scoundrel!

141
00:08:20,279 --> 00:08:22,360
It happened so suddenly, a momentary slip.

142
00:08:23,319 --> 00:08:24,000
Ning Chen.

143
00:08:24,560 --> 00:08:27,079
Eunuch Quan acted out of loyalty to protect Us,

144
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:28,759
and in his haste he wounded you.

145
00:08:29,079 --> 00:08:30,199
Do not hold it against him.

146
00:08:32,799 --> 00:08:33,399
We know

147
00:08:33,799 --> 00:08:35,360
you've long wished to leave the Ning estate.

148
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:36,320
How about this:

149
00:08:36,960 --> 00:08:38,200
When you return from the border,

150
00:08:38,519 --> 00:08:40,120
We shall grant you a manor,

151
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:42,279
a hundred acres of land, and ten thousand taels of gold.

152
00:08:42,759 --> 00:08:43,360
How does that sound?

153
00:08:45,759 --> 00:08:47,440
And what if I die at the border?

154
00:08:49,159 --> 00:08:51,120
Who curses themselves like that?

155
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:53,440
Blades show no mercy,

156
00:08:55,799 --> 00:08:56,360
Your Majesty.

157
00:08:58,080 --> 00:08:59,080
If by chance

158
00:08:59,679 --> 00:09:01,000
something truly happens to me

159
00:09:01,960 --> 00:09:02,639
and I cannot return,

160
00:09:06,720 --> 00:09:07,679
I beg Your Majesty to permit

161
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:09,279
Lady Yudie of the Music Bureau

162
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:10,399
to be restored to freedom.

163
00:09:11,080 --> 00:09:12,519
The manor Your Majesty promised me,

164
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:13,320
along with the land,

165
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:14,679
please bestow upon Lady Yudie.

166
00:09:15,159 --> 00:09:15,840
As for the gold,

167
00:09:16,559 --> 00:09:17,919
please grant it to my brothers,

168
00:09:18,720 --> 00:09:19,600
and let them divide it.

169
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:26,159
You truly are a man of loyalty and affection.

170
00:09:26,519 --> 00:09:27,759
You've arranged it all quite nicely.

171
00:09:27,960 --> 00:09:29,840
But We will not agree to it.

172
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:30,480
On the contrary,

173
00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:33,080
if you fail to crawl back alive to see Us,

174
00:09:33,480 --> 00:09:35,159
then We shall take that

175
00:09:35,279 --> 00:09:37,080
beloved Lady Yudie of yours

176
00:09:37,960 --> 00:09:39,639
and have her killed to join you below.

177
00:09:39,960 --> 00:09:41,519
A sovereign does not jest.

178
00:09:42,559 --> 00:09:43,039
I...

179
00:09:43,639 --> 00:09:44,480
I... well...

180
00:09:44,919 --> 00:09:46,159
Is this gun easy to make?

181
00:09:50,840 --> 00:09:51,480
It's easy.

182
00:09:52,279 --> 00:09:53,279
But only easy for me.

183
00:09:53,960 --> 00:09:55,519
For others, well,

184
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:56,799
without knowing the principles,

185
00:09:57,120 --> 00:09:58,279
even if they make the parts,

186
00:09:58,480 --> 00:09:59,159
if they can't assemble them,

187
00:10:00,480 --> 00:10:01,000
it's useless.

188
00:10:01,600 --> 00:10:04,320
What if We demand you hand over

189
00:10:04,720 --> 00:10:06,159
the methods for its production and assembly?

190
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:12,720
This thing here

191
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:14,519
was always meant as a gift to Your Majesty.

192
00:10:15,159 --> 00:10:16,759
Your Majesty may select a portion of the troops,

193
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:19,000
arm them with muskets, and form a firearms corps.

194
00:10:19,559 --> 00:10:21,440
Muskets are devastating against cavalry.

195
00:10:21,919 --> 00:10:23,159
With a single bullet fired,

196
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:25,639
I guarantee twice the result for half the effort.

197
00:10:27,039 --> 00:10:29,120
It seems you've already planned

198
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:31,960
to use this against the Tuoluo cavalry.

199
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:32,799
Yes indeed.

200
00:10:34,200 --> 00:10:34,840
Good.

201
00:10:35,360 --> 00:10:36,799
Then We approve it.

202
00:10:37,639 --> 00:10:39,000
But have you considered,

203
00:10:39,320 --> 00:10:40,840
if this weapon is leaked,

204
00:10:41,240 --> 00:10:43,399
the consequences would be unthinkable.

205
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:45,120
Rest assured, Your Majesty.

206
00:10:45,320 --> 00:10:45,799
By then,

207
00:10:47,159 --> 00:10:49,320
I'll have built even more powerful firearms.

208
00:10:51,080 --> 00:10:51,799
It seems

209
00:10:52,639 --> 00:10:54,519
this isn't the only one you've mastered.

210
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:56,720
At such a young age,

211
00:10:57,679 --> 00:10:58,879
brimming with talent,

212
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:00,120
full of wit and resourcefulness.

213
00:11:00,639 --> 00:11:01,480
We were just thinking,

214
00:11:01,840 --> 00:11:03,240
if you'd been born in an enemy state,

215
00:11:03,440 --> 00:11:04,360
you would be

216
00:11:04,840 --> 00:11:07,399
Great Xuan's most terrifying enemy.

217
00:11:12,240 --> 00:11:13,360
A gentleman dies for the one who appreciates him,

218
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:15,200
and a woman adorns herself for the one who loves her.

219
00:11:16,480 --> 00:11:18,240
Your Majesty's discerning eye discovered me,

220
00:11:18,679 --> 00:11:19,919
and gave me such a grand

221
00:11:20,080 --> 00:11:21,120
stage to showcase my abilities.

222
00:11:21,799 --> 00:11:23,480
I am deeply grateful,

223
00:11:23,919 --> 00:11:24,759
and shall keep it engraved in my heart.

224
00:11:25,639 --> 00:11:26,600
For Your Majesty, I am willing

225
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:30,000
to climb mountains of blades and seas of fire,

226
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:31,120
to brave any peril,

227
00:11:31,320 --> 00:11:32,440
and would not hesitate even if it meant ten thousand deaths.

228
00:11:39,480 --> 00:11:40,000
Good.

229
00:11:40,960 --> 00:11:41,960
Well said.

230
00:11:43,919 --> 00:11:44,559
You may withdraw.

231
00:11:46,320 --> 00:11:47,360
I take my leave.

232
00:11:55,320 --> 00:11:56,039
Shipeng.

233
00:11:56,639 --> 00:11:57,360
Do you realize

234
00:11:57,919 --> 00:11:58,639
that this firearm

235
00:11:58,960 --> 00:12:02,759
is a lifesaver for Great Xuan's mighty army?

236
00:12:03,679 --> 00:12:04,639
A boon for the present,

237
00:12:05,440 --> 00:12:06,600
and a legacy for the ages.

238
00:12:08,679 --> 00:12:09,639
That silly lad,

239
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:12,159
he didn't even think to ask Us for a reward.

240
00:12:13,559 --> 00:12:15,759
Hasn't he just joined the Imperial Inspectorate?

241
00:12:16,159 --> 00:12:17,320
He probably hasn't received his stipend yet.

242
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:20,960
Then bestow upon him a hundred bolts of fine silk

243
00:12:21,200 --> 00:12:22,320
and a thousand taels of gold.

244
00:12:22,720 --> 00:12:23,200
How does that sound?

245
00:12:24,000 --> 00:12:26,039
Ning Chen has a youthful temperament.

246
00:12:26,559 --> 00:12:28,720
Might he grow arrogant from such favor?

247
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:30,799
Arrogant? Let him be arrogant.

248
00:12:31,080 --> 00:12:33,559
For a once-in-a-century talent like Ning Chen,

249
00:12:33,720 --> 00:12:35,320
even We feel proud on his behalf.

250
00:12:36,759 --> 00:12:37,440
Now go, quickly.

251
00:12:38,039 --> 00:12:38,720
As you command.

252
00:12:42,799 --> 00:12:44,799
A mere youngster like Ning Chen,

253
00:12:45,600 --> 00:12:48,720
yet he's turned the capital upside down.

254
00:12:49,559 --> 00:12:50,320
It seems

255
00:12:50,919 --> 00:12:52,960
I truly underestimated him.

